      "patchset_number": 2,
      "line": 12,
      "message": "OOM-1676 rolling upgrade also includes Common Cassandra OOM-1652, OOM-1186 and OOM-1187.\nShould reference all the cases.\nIncluding the shared Cassandra seems premature, given that the AAI team has not fully considered the impacts of changing this basic assumption nor considered the possibility of clashes with other teams and their usage of Cassandra.",
