      "file_path": "kubernetes/aai/charts/aai-graphadmin/templates/job.yaml",
      "patchset_number": 2,
      "line": 149,
      "message": "As this is one time job (So doesnt change anything on the normal graphadmin pod), it would use the datasnapshot present on this volume which is a PV and restore it. The snapshot would be taken by the backup job and will be saved on PV.\n\nEven in case of shared cassandra, we are using the janusgraph to connect to it so it doesnt matter where the underlying cassandra cluster is. We are working on a particular keyspace.",
      "author": {
        "account_id": 2763,
        "name": "Mahendra Raghuwanshi",
        "display_name": null,
        "email": "mahendra.raghuwanshi@amdocs.com",
        "username": "mahendrr"
